      "originalText": "Cron job [Issue with this approach]\n- checks DB\n- more than 10 mins\n- change those which are reserved\n but not booked back to available\n- has a problem: introduces delta : \nbetween time cron job ran and changed status \nback to available",
      "autoResize": true,
